<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="first-adj">first <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɜːst/    美 /fɜːrst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>第一 (位) 的；最前面的；最初的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His second book is better than his first.
他的第二本书比第一本要好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>in the first few days 
在最初几天里</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in the first place</strong> 
起初；首先</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>First impressions are half the battle.
先入为主。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>首要的；最重要的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an issue of first importance
首要问题</p></div></div>